=Skriv Markup=

Interpreter of the Skriv Markup Language. PHP implementation.

==How to use it==
You need to install the [[http://github.com/Amaury/wikirenderer|PSR version]] of [[http://github.com/laurentj/wikirenderer|WikiRenderer]].

These libraries are PSR-0-compatible, so you'll also need an autoloader. You can use the [[https://github.com/Amaury/FineBase/blob/master/lib/FineAutoload.php|FineAutoload]] object from [[https://github.com/Amaury/FineBase|FineBase]].
{{{
<?php
 require_once('finebase/FineAutoload.php');
 FineAutoload::autoload();

 $cfg = new \Skriv\Markup\Config();
 $wikiRenderer = new \WikiRenderer\Renderer($cfg);
 $html = $wikiRenderer->render($wikiString);
?>
}}}

